            <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    View Orders
                    <p>From the REPORTS tab, this shows a table of all orders places by students for products. It has the First Name, Last Name, and Order Date. </p>
                    <p>
                        To go to page click
                        <em><b><u><a href="/Order">View Orders</a></b></u></em>
                    </p>

                    <div id="report1"> Report 1 </div>
                    <p>From the REPORTS tab, this page displays a report detailing each student’s First Name, Last Name, and Cumulative Point Total. </p>
                    <p>
                        To go to page click
                        <em><b><u><a href="/Report">Report 1</a></b></u></em>
                    </p>

                    <div id="report2"> Report 2 </div>
                    <p>From the REPORTS tab, This page displays a report detailing all student information. </p>
